title: The First Years On-the-Go Booster Seat Only $13.40
text:
Head on over to Walmart.com , Jet.com or Amazon.com (Prime members only) and grab this The First Years On-the-Go Booster Seat for only $13.40 (regularly $20.99). *Please note that the seat is available in Safari Print from Walmart and Amazon while Jet is offering the item in Blue Dinosaur Print. 
This seat self-inflates into a sturdy and comfortable full-size booster seat for kiddos from 9 months old and up to 50 pounds. It has a handle to make it easy to take along on the go and the adjustable safety belt with restraint keeps little ones secure in the seat.
Shipping Options Walmart: Choose free in-store pick up if available near you; otherwise, score FREE 2-day shipping on any eligible $35+ order or pay $5.99 for shipping for orders under $35.
Amazon: This item is a Prime Member Exclusive and ships free with membership.
Jet: Shipping is free on orders over $35 before discounts. If you’re a new Jet.com member, you’ll save an additional 15% off your first three orders of $35 or more when you enter promo code TRIPLE15 at checkout.
